    <p>Nuun is the brand that revolutionized portable electrolyte supplementation with its effervescent tablets, and their gummy format extends that expertise. With 200mg sodium per serving and a decade of trust among endurance athletes (marathon runners, triathletes, ultra-runners), Nuun delivers a proven electrolyte profile in the convenience of gummy format. The B Corp certification adds ethical sourcing and sustainability credibility. For endurance athletes who already trust Nuun's tablet products, the gummies provide an additional format option for race day and training.</p>

